divs: Sighting DetailsMy husband and I were out at a lake picnicing and decided to take pictures of birds. I had spotted a nest with a bird flying around and decided to pull to the side of the road to take a picture of a bird that had landed on top of a post. Didn't had time until weeks later to put the pictures on my computer when afterward noticed something strange in the background. After using zoombrowser on the picture,we couldn't identify what it was.Hoping someone might be able to give us some sort of insight.Picture enclosed.
Summary: Taking pictures of birds, nice eagle,get home, download two weeks later, hey, whats that black line...
